{"image_id": "ZBRA_2014_page_47", "image_size": [1650, 1275], "ocr": [{"text": "F-13", "bbox": [1556.7, 1223.3, 1575.0, 1238.5]}, {"text": "Note 5 Investments and Marketable Securities", "bbox": [87.5, 146.8, 505.2, 166.7]}, {"text": "Investments in marketable debt securities are classified based on intent and ability to", "bbox": [87.5, 167.6, 781.4, 187.8]}, {"text": "sell investment securities. Zebra’s available-for-sale securities are used to fund future", "bbox": [87.5, 188.5, 783.7, 208.7]}, {"text": "acquisitions and other operating needs and therefore can be sold prior to maturity.", "bbox": [87.5, 209.3, 761.3, 229.5]}, {"text": "Investments in marketable debt securities for which Zebra intends to sell within the next", "bbox": [87.5, 230.1, 805.2, 250.3]}, {"text": "year are classified as current and those that we intend to hold in excess of one-year are", "bbox": [87.5, 251.0, 794.7, 271.2]}, {"text": "classified as non-current.", "bbox": [87.5, 271.8, 292.0, 292.0]}, {"text": "Changes in the market value of available-for-sale securities are reflected in the", "bbox": [87.5, 311.4, 724.7, 331.6]}, {"text": "accumulated other comprehensive income caption of stockholders’ equity in the balance", "bbox": [87.5, 332.2, 810.0, 352.4]}, {"text": "sheet, until we dispose of the securities. Once these securities are disposed of, either by", "bbox": [87.5, 353.1, 803.9, 373.2]}, {"text": "sale or maturity, the accumulated changes in market value are transferred to investment", "bbox": [87.5, 373.9, 804.5, 394.1]}, {"text": "income. On the Consolidated Statement of Cash Flows, changes in the balances of", "bbox": [87.5, 394.7, 757.2, 414.9]}, {"text": "available-for-sale securities are shown as purchases, sales and maturities of investments", "bbox": [87.5, 415.6, 809.8, 435.7]}, {"text": "and marketable securities under investing activities.", "bbox": [87.5, 436.4, 514.0, 456.6]}, {"text": "Changes in market value of trading securities would be recorded in investment income", "bbox": [856.3, 169.0, 1560.7, 189.2]}, {"text": "as they occur, and the related cash flow statement includes changes in the balances of", "bbox": [856.3, 189.9, 1557.6, 210.1]}, {"text": "trading securities as operating cash flows.", "bbox": [856.3, 210.7, 1198.0, 230.9]}, {"text": "Changes in unrealized gains and losses on available-for-sale securities are included in", "bbox": [856.3, 250.3, 1547.0, 270.5]}, {"text": "these financial statements as follows (in thousands):", "bbox": [856.3, 271.1, 1275.3, 291.3]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31,", "bbox": [1298.0, 302.3, 1512.5, 320.0]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [1259.8, 323.2, 1302.8, 340.5]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [1393.1, 323.2, 1436.1, 340.5]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [1518.0, 323.2, 1556.3, 340.5]}, {"text": "Changes in unrealized gains and losses", "bbox": [856.3, 348.2, 1174.5, 368.4]}, {"text": "on available-for-sale securities, net of tax,", "bbox": [856.3, 369.0, 1209.4, 389.2]}, {"text": "recorded in accumulated other", "bbox": [856.3, 389.9, 1120.9, 410.1]}, {"text": "comprehensive income (loss)", "bbox": [856.3, 410.7, 1109.8, 430.9]}, {"text": "$425", "bbox": [1260.2, 410.7, 1302.5, 430.9]}, {"text": "$(456)", "bbox": [1390.0, 410.7, 1443.4, 430.9]}, {"text": "$887", "bbox": [1517.7, 410.7, 1556.3, 430.9]}, {"text": "The following table shows the number, aggregate market value and unrealized losses (in thousands) of investments with market values that were less than amortized cost as of December 31,", "bbox": [87.5, 522.2, 1577.7, 542.3]}, {"text": "2014. These lower market values are primarily caused by fluctuations in interest rates and credit spreads. Market values are expected to recover to the amortized cost prior to maturity.", "bbox": [87.5, 543.0, 1524.3, 563.2]}, {"text": "Unrealized Loss < 12 months", "bbox": [572.2, 580.1, 804.9, 597.5]}, {"text": "Unrealized Loss > 12 months", "bbox": [1190.9, 580.1, 1418.8, 597.5]}, {"text": "Number of", "bbox": [453.2, 603.0, 547.1, 62